4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper uses online videos on YouTube as a data source for learning view extrapolation. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper proposes a deep network for predicting multiplane images.
